The motherboard itself isn't what's actually offering the GPU capability -- your CPU is what does.  Intel's GMA is integrated into some models of CPUs as I'm sure you know, so the issue may be related to GPU drivers.  Gigabyte Technical Support should be able to help you with this.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3">koitsu</a> — Sun Sep 01, 2013 9:13 am</p><hr />
